OL,4,CContactless card limit to rise to #100
OL,5,Cin October
OL,6, The spending limit on each use of a
OL,7, contactless card is to rise from #45 to
OL,8, #100 from 15 October, banks have
OL,9, revealed.
OL,11,FThe maximum amount was increased from
OL,12,F#30 to its current level at the start
OL,13,Fof the pandemic, and plans to raise it
OL,14,Ffurther were announced in the Budget.
OL,16,FNearly two-thirds of all debit card
OL,17,Ftransactions are made via the
OL,18,Ftap-and-go technology.
OL,20,FBut academics have warned that raising
OL,21,Fthe limit could increase crime.
